Title: TicTacToeTah
Description: TicTacToeTah is a new twist on TicTacToe which requires you to think in three dimensions.  Built using C# and WPF.  It supports playing against your friends either locally or online and also has a challenging computer artifical intelligence.
HomeWiki:
About

TicTacToeTah is a new twist on TicTacToe which requires you to think in three dimensions. Built using C# and WPF. It supports playing against your friends either locally or online and also has a challenging computer artifical intelligence.

Interesting Fact

Infact there are 76 different ways to win!
